description: Amazon Kendra now provides a data source connector for Slack. For more information, see https://docs.aws.amazon.com/kendra/latest/dg/data-source-slack.html
Amazon Timestream Scheduled Queries now support Timestamp datatype in a multi-measure record.
Added support for modeled exception fields when adding errors to a client stub. Implements boto/boto3`#3178 <https://github.com/boto/botocore/issues/3178>`__.
Add resourceType enums for AWS::ECR::PublicRepository and AWS::EC2::LaunchTemplate
